= Downloads =

*Running OLED:*

OLED is multi-plataform, so the available .jar will run on Windows, Mac OS and Linux .

To run it, simply *double-click* on the jar file, or type *java -jar oled-1.0.05.jar* in a console (*Java 7 or superior* -- download Java [https://java.com/download here]).
